## Core Roles Configuration

### Roles to Create

{%- if scim_prefix | upper != 'NONE' %}
{%- set owner_role = scim_prefix | upper ~ '_PROVISIONER' %}
{%- else %}
{%- set owner_role = 'USERADMIN' %}
{%- endif %}

| Role | Name | Purpose | Owner |
|------|------|---------|-------|
| **ADMIN** | `{{ data_product_name | upper }}_ADMIN` | Owns infrastructure (databases, schemas, warehouses) | `{{ owner_role }}` |
| **CREATE** | `{{ data_product_name | upper }}_CREATE` | Creates objects, receives account access roles | `{{ owner_role }}` |
| **WRITE** | `{{ data_product_name | upper }}_WRITE` | Modifies data (DML operations) | `{{ owner_role }}` |
| **RBAC** | `{{ data_product_name | upper }}_RBAC` | Owns access roles for delegated governance | `{{ owner_role }}` |
| **READ** | `{{ data_product_name | upper }}_READ` | Read-only access to data product | `{{ owner_role }}` |

### Role Hierarchy

```
SYSADMIN
└── {{ data_product_name | upper }}_ADMIN
    ├── {{ data_product_name | upper }}_CREATE
    │   ├── _AR_EXEC_TASK (execute tasks)
    │   ├── _AR_VIEW_AUSG (view account usage)
    │   ├── _AR_APPLY_DDM (apply masking policies)
    │   ├── _AR_APPLY_RAP (apply row access policies)
    │   └── _AR_APPLY_TAG (apply tags)
    └── {{ data_product_name | upper }}_RBAC
```

### SCIM Configuration

{%- if scim_prefix | upper != 'NONE' %}
| Setting | Value |
|---------|-------|
| **SCIM Enabled** | Yes |
| **SCIM Prefix** | `{{ scim_prefix | upper }}` |
| **Role Owner** | `{{ scim_prefix | upper }}_PROVISIONER` |
| **User Assignment** | Via identity provider groups |

> **Note:** After roles are created, configure your identity provider ({{ scim_prefix }}) to map groups to these roles for automatic user assignment.
{%- else %}
| Setting | Value |
|---------|-------|
| **SCIM Enabled** | No |
| **Role Owner** | `USERADMIN` |
| **User Assignment** | Manual GRANT statements |

> **Note:** Use `GRANT ROLE <role> TO USER <user>` to assign users to these roles.
{%- endif %}

### Account Access Roles

The following account access roles will be granted to `{{ data_product_name | upper }}_CREATE`:

| Access Role | Purpose |
|-------------|---------|
| `_AR_EXEC_TASK` | Execute Snowflake tasks (scheduled jobs) |
| `_AR_VIEW_AUSG` | View Account Usage data for monitoring |
| `_AR_APPLY_DDM` | Apply dynamic data masking policies |
| `_AR_APPLY_RAP` | Apply row access policies |
| `_AR_APPLY_TAG` | Apply tags to objects |

> **Note:** These roles must exist in the account. If they don't exist, the grants will be skipped with warnings.
